#. type: delimited block -
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/qute.adoc:56
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/qute.adoc:118
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/qute.adoc:153
#: upstream/_versions/2.2/guides/qute.adoc:181
